{"tid":1331181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]緊急！大埔連儂隧道！","createTime":"2019-07-19T00:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T00:28:50.000Z","uid":272600,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"be26fbca0ec2ed064e173c55334a4fc10d11ff77","tid":1331181,"uid":272600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T00:22:49.000Z","msg":"作為廢中，岩岩收到另一個住大埔既廢中朋友消息。<br />\n有個女學生整緊連儂隧道時比兩個老年人圍罵。<br />\n希望有附近既巴絲可以去解圍，或幫幫佢重建連儂隧道。<br />\n至於無幫人既廢中，我叫左佢每做龜一次，課番300買物資。佢都應承左，或者大家負評爆佢，謝謝。"},{"pid":"65c1e14853444e57fc45d9faabf197220cf94aba","tid":1331181,"uid":69525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T00:24:03.000Z","msg":"如果大家去書展既話順便做埋文宣！<br />\n咁多人流 慢慢send<br />\n<br />\n人人都可以做文宣<br />\n善用Airdrop<br />\n 首先 設定&gt;一般&gt;關於本機 改個靚名<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q1vJw5M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ1vJw5M.png&h=75f30bb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再揀圖send出去 <br />\n重點強調 20/7沒有任何遊行 同 <br />\n大大力宣傳21/7 改返做維園為集合點 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HRpRFZy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHRpRFZy.png&h=f04a049e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ORsYMd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ORsYMd.png&h=1456c573&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CYH7YMe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCYH7YMe.png&h=5e0d2be9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8cvhBxU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8cvhBxU.png&h=ee07484f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h15hBxV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh15hBxV.png&h=69a8630b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"388ce033b7563acc5f922f9af1221c1e11e30a70","tid":1331181,"uid":272600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T00:28:50.000Z","msg":"推"}]}